66
00:04:24,075 --> 00:04:26,411
- Thanks. Thanks...
- Such a unique voice.

67
00:04:26,578 --> 00:04:29,205
Boy, I'd love to find
a portal into your brain.

68
00:04:29,372 --> 00:04:31,166
Trust me, it's no fun.

69
00:04:33,418 --> 00:04:36,379
So tell me your thoughts
on this crazy little project of ours.

70
00:04:38,506 --> 00:04:40,175
First, I think it's a great book.

71
00:04:41,634 --> 00:04:43,845
- Laroche is a fun character, isn't he?
- Absolutely.

72
00:04:44,012 --> 00:04:47,265
And Orlean makes orchids
so fascinating.

73
00:04:47,432 --> 00:04:50,977
Plus, her musings on Florida
and orchid poaching...

74
00:04:51,144 --> 00:04:54,397
