sprawling New Yorker stuff.

75
00:04:54,564 --> 00:04:56,191
I'd want to remain true to that.

76
00:04:56,358 --> 00:05:00,320
I'd wanna let the movie exist,
rather than be...

77
00:05:00,487 --> 00:05:03,865
...artificially plot-driven.
- Great.

78
00:05:04,824 --> 00:05:06,951
I guess I'm not exactly sure
what that means.

79
00:05:09,829 --> 00:05:12,582
I'm not sure I know
what that means either.

80
00:05:12,749 --> 00:05:15,794
